Initialize ESP32
Initialize DHT11
Initialize LDR
Initialize LCD
Initialize Heater LED
Initialize Fan LED
Initialize Grow Light LED
Initialize MQTT
Loop
Read Temperature
Read Humidity
Read LDR Value
Calculate Running Average of Last 10 LDR Readings
If Temperature < 18
Turn ON Heater
Turn OFF Fan
Else If Temperature > 22
Turn ON Fan
Turn OFF Heater
Else
Turn OFF Heater
Turn OFF Fan
End If
If Light Level is Low
Turn ON Grow Light
Else
Turn OFF Grow Light
End If
Display Temperature
Display Humidity
Display Light Level
Publish Data to MQTT
Wait 3 Seconds
Repeat
